    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a trivial modification to the ARP mechanism, not the packet format, which allows a node to announce that it is leaving the network and that all other nodes should modify their ARP tables accordingly.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
